{
  "stem": "7414.7",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then a door from a carriage opens, and the German in a uniform opens the door and tells me come in into a German wagon, beautifully lit, and there were perhaps five or six people in the whole-- warm, dry.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was sitting there next to a woman in a beautiful fur coat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she had all the food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She had the thermos flask, and she started to feed the baby.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so I come to my destination.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I will tell you, I-- sometimes I think myself, I must have looked very helpless.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was very small, very thin at this time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And like a man who was not far from me, he looked at me, and he told me, give me the baby, we'll help you.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A child carries a child, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was-- really I looked like a small child. back then.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They must have really-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] because I was really helped by so many people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, we came to this nation, we came to this place, and there started a bit of a time not when as she somehow, she looked at me and she disliked me.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One of the few people who really-- she took a dislike-- This is Auntie Paula's--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Cousin.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But she could not turn me out because I was the cousin.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so we were there together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Luckily, there was, in the neighboring room, was a young couple from Lodz, which had a baby-- a few months old baby-- and we got very friendly.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were really my-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] no, how you tell?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not only cover, but they gave me a bit of moral support.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not did they knew that I am Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But anyway, we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
